formattedAddress: Lv 3. Swissôtel the Stamford (2 Stamford Rd.)

tip.text: Order the onion rings - Fried and caramelized to perfection! Buffalo wings and Lucy burger was pretty good, though they should cook patties to medium rather than well done.
Tried the matcha tart and dark chocolate dessert (with an ice-cream stick). Both were excellent. However, note that there is a NT150 minimum spend per person in order to be seated.
